{"tid":484925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【體壇性侵】馬會騎術教練遭解僱","createTime":"2017-11-30T13:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T16:46:48.000Z","uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf8d3ae1b24238b11becd87c2553c5765e632e5","tid":484925,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1078691/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1078691%2F&d=0Bz1V8xRapYNRm7s%2FTaqVjANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=1544d2c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1078691%2F&h=fafc9cd4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1078691/</a><br />\n<br />\n【體壇性侵】涉性騷擾青少年馬術隊成員 馬會騎術教練遭解僱<br />\n<br />\n香港跨欄女子運動員呂麗瑤爆出曾被前教練性侵犯後，體育、演藝、文化及出版界立法會議員馬逢國透露，兩周前收到涉及體育界其他性侵個案的匿名舉報。香港賽馬會晚上證實，曾接獲馬逢國及其他人士，對青少年馬術隊成員被性騷擾的查詢。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，馬會一向高度重視員工的道德操守，並以非常嚴肅的態度處理有關查詢，即時向相關人士展開詳細調查。調查結果顯示，一名騎術教練在執行職務期間，曾使用涉及性騷擾的不當用語，馬會因而在本月24日解僱該名騎術教練。<br />\n<br />\n馬會強調，會嚴正處理所有涉及員工操守的指控，絕不容忍任何違反員工守則的行為。"},{"pid":"861b315e11ea563fc6e494073b11f6fb0bb41156","tid":484925,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:26:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6feec9c694221a8145b77e9080f08b378ee91414","tid":484925,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"又多一單"},{"pid":"dac6336b313be578e871f395f01502a9ea0b32ec","tid":484925,"uid":33176,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾使用涉及性騷擾的<span style=\"color: red;\">不當用語</span></blockquote><br />\nCLS, 可能只係屌吓人老母<br />\n咁都坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33394106ae1c5bb3efe90683ee80a05762119a0c","tid":484925,"uid":62888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"r